valueProp:
This firm is a well-known and highly respected business attorney providing quality, affordable business legal services. Valerie Kramer, the lead attorney, has 30 years of experience setting up incorporations, LLCs, writing contracts, and handling business disputes and lawsuits. The firm specializes in debt collection, business formation, contract disputes, partnership disputes, and real estate law.

The experienced team at this firm is dedicated to helping individuals and small business owners in San Diego and Orange Counties with their legal needs. With a focus on business law, debt collection, incorporation, and real estate matters, they provide expert guidance and representation to ensure their clients' interests are protected and their legal issues are resolved effectively.
